OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome evening
OL,6,Fsunshine away from the far north, then
OL,7,Fthe cloud there will extend south
OL,8,Facross much of the region tonight,
OL,9,Fwith the odd light shower. Lochaber
OL,10,Fstaying clear.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy start for most, the
OL,13,Fodd light shower, but sunnier over
OL,14,FLochaber, and all areas will brighten
OL,15,Fup with some good sunny spells in the
OL,16,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
