OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells on Sunday, then cloudier in
OL,7,Fnorthwest with light rain later.
OL,8,FCloudy start Monday then most areas
OL,9,Fbrightening up with some sunshine.
OL,10,FNorthwest cloudy, damp Tuesday,
OL,11,Fsunshine elsewhere.
